{"tid":2223498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國2.96億網民　 月入千元或以下","createTime":"2020-09-30T01:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T01:34:14.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"79a01a03c4634cae955360c1f4dcb6a9cc18ecaa","tid":2223498,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f3knZI2Mx-ZGMe9ZH709-rJuLiU=/1446x780/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VV6ZWQP3PFD6XKVO5GNXOY5CDA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff3knZI2Mx-ZGMe9ZH709-rJuLiU%3D%2F1446x780%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVV6ZWQP3PFD6XKVO5GNXOY5CDA.gif&h=7ef042e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VkBsOMIYD4hNAs5Phr-T1OGTsNc=/1241x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PSY3H6KDLBCTBEFCPRHGUHRAXI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVkBsOMIYD4hNAs5Phr-T1OGTsNc%3D%2F1241x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPSY3H6KDLBCTBEFCPRHGUHRAXI.jpg&h=e6178ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■數字揭示越來越多低收入人士上網。<br />\n...<br />\n越來越多低收入人士上網<br />\n今年5月底，中國國務院總理李克強在2020年兩會期間的記者會上提到「有6億人每個月的收入也就1,000元人民幣」，引發社會熱議。《報告》指出，截至今年6月，月入1,000元或以下的網民有2.96億人，佔全體網民的31.5%；此項數據於今年3月則為27.9%，2019年6月為26.4%，2018年12月為22.6%。可見月入低於1,000元的網民佔比越來越大，反映出越來越多低收入人士能夠上網。<br />\n報告另首次提到中國國家主席習近平今年8月提到的「內循環」經濟。報告指出，網絡購物等數字消費，為推動經濟內循環提供了新動力。上半年，網絡零售用戶規模達7.49億，佔網民整體的79.7%，連續七年保持全球第一，同時超過社會消費品零售總額的四分之一，對消費的支撐作用進一步增強。報告顯示，生鮮電商、農產品電商、跨境電商、二手電商等電商新模式也保持較快發展，用戶規模分別達到2.57億、2.48億、1.38億和6,143萬。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200930/SHLANH2F7FHUVFJ755GXMGCO4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200930%2FSHLANH2F7FHUVFJ755GXMGCO4U%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWBlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=a16981b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200930%2FSHLANH2F7FHUVFJ755GXMGCO4U%2F&h=1109f780\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200930/SHLANH2F7FHUVFJ755GXMGCO4U/</a>"},{"pid":"94eae0419965b5d65ecbee8fe605033ed58d3507","tid":2223498,"uid":309585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T01:34:14.000Z","msg":"個基數都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}